rows.label: tlk43400012_03_msg0001
rows.name:
I knew the Special Distribution Audit
Bureau had made a move, but I never
thought they'd beat me to the punch.

rows.label: tlk43400012_03_msg0002
rows.name:
That Nilny bloke's really
got his head screwed on.

rows.label: tlk43400012_03_msg0003
rows.name:
If only he hadn't sold out to
Superbia, we'd have got our hands
on our slippery little chairman...

rows.label: tlk43400012_03_msg0004
rows.name:
In any case, I'll have to
report back to Invidia.

rows.label: tlk43400012_03_msg0005
rows.name:
Will it really be over,
though? Will the corruption
really end with Bahn?
